items.title: NORMAL VALUES
items.description:
• Haemoglobin : 12-16 gm/ dL
  • Blood Sugar : Fasting – less than 100 mg / dL
  • Post prandial – less than 140 mg/dL
  • Blood urea Nitrogen 8 to 20 ml/dL
  • Creatinine 0.7 to 1.3 ml/dL
  • TSH – 0.5 to5.0 mU/ml
  • Prolactin – less than 23 ng/ml
  • FSH ( day 2 to day 5) – 3.5 to 12.5 pg/ml
  • LH ( day 2 to day 5) – 2.4 to 12.6 mIU/ml
  • AMH 1.3 to 3.0 ng/ml
  • HbSAg, HIV – ve for non-reactive.
